danfulea.phys

Class GammaDetector

  • java.lang.Object
    • danfulea.phys.GammaDetector

  • public class GammaDetector
extends java.lang.Object
    Compute gamma detector efficiency using KERMA approximation. Since the geometry is cylindrical, i.e. RZ geometry, a much better approach is using EGSnrc (or GEANT4) toolkit. Therefore, most methods of this class are deprecated.
    Author:
    Dan Fulea, 2005
